==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Phrensy
<hw>Phren"sy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Violent and
irrational excitement; delirium. See <er>Frenzy</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Phrensy</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Phrensy
<hw>Phren"sy</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To render frantic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Phrentic</ent>⟦br⟧
